    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction has been reviewed. Despite multiple credibility factor gaps at MRL 5, the assessment package is accepted as a complete documentation of the current credibility state. The decision reflects acceptance of the assessment process and documentation, not acceptance of the model for regulatory submission. Remediation actions have been identified for all assessed factors below required levels and all six not-assessed factors.",
